            "title": "Dickey's offering Tailgating Box for $120 on National Tailgating Day with smoked wings, ribs, and sides.",
            "id": "9b0c8cb9-ced2-4fd2-b8a8-516bf7e7b360",
            "description": "In preparation for National Tailgating Day on September 6, Dickey’s Barbecue Pit in Dallas is offering a special Tailgating Box deal for $120. This offer includes a delectable assortment of smoked wings, ribs, and traditional barbecue sides, all prepared with Dickey’s renowned pit-smoked expertise. This promotion is tailored towards football enthusiasts, families, and those hosting backyard gatherings. The aim is to enhance the communal experience of tailgating by providing a delicious spread that caters to a variety of tastes.",
